tuc.ece.cs202.project2

Class BSTAttribution

  • java.lang.Object
    • tuc.ece.cs202.project2.BSTAttribution

  • public class BSTAttribution
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the main class of the program.

    It operates the methods of three data structures

    1. Dynamic Binary Search Trees

    2. Static Binary Search Trees

    3. Sorted Arrays

    Some of the operations of this class are:

    1. It inserts new data in the data structures

    2. It searches for a key in the data structures

    3. It searches for a range of keys in the data structures

    4. It measures the time elapsed for a number of insertions

    5. It measures the time elapsed for a number of searches

    Author:
    Georgios Frangias
